---
title: Spiced Swedish Meatballs with Mushrooms and Fusilli
description: These traditional Swedish meatballs are flavoured with warm spices like allspice and nutmeg and sweetened with a touch of dried cranberries! Tossed in a light cream sauce, this comfort food classic is great for any weeknight meal.
